{"tid":386104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台在晚上十時四十分改發三號強風信號","createTime":"2017-09-03T15:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T11:47:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f5a23f2f08d3ab7d1dbd967b6e1e3e110dfe952","tid":386104,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=234678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D234678&d=Y%2F%2Fv4f0f0VXBx9ckt%2B6JkV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2d076ed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D234678&h=37f7761a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=234678</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】熱帶風暴「瑪娃」已經在廣東汕尾登陸，隨着瑪娃進一步接近本港，天文台在晚上十時四十分改發三號強風信號。<br />\n<br />\n本港晚上風勢不大，市民逛街時沒有撐傘。天文台表示，與瑪娃相關的雨帶會影響珠三角一帶，預料星期一初段時間本港會有狂風大雨。"},{"pid":"78fb9b008d3fc9459aadaef4d48d304abf52f095","tid":386104,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}